                                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
                                <span><strong>Oracle SQL</strong> - Complex PL/SQL, performance tuning</span>
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center">
                                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3"></span>
